===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|s=干|alt=亁,乹,漧}}

From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*kan|t=to dry; to dry up}}. Cognate with {{och-l|旱|drought}}, {{cog|my|ခန်း||to dry up; to evaporate}} (STEDT).

The sense “lacking sweetness” is a {{semantic loan|zh|fr|sec|nocap=1}} or {{semantic loan|zh|en|dry|notext=1}}.

